page_title: Azure OpenAI on your Azure Cosmos DB data Python & REST API reference
page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI on your Azure Cosmos DB data Python & REST API.
chunk_content: Deployment name vectorization sourceThe details of the vectorization source, used by Azure OpenAI On Your Data when applying vector search. This vectorization source is based on an internal embeddings model deployment name in the same Azure OpenAI resource. This vectorization source enables you to use vector search without Azure OpenAI api-key and without Azure OpenAI public network access.|Name | Type | Required | Description ||--- | --- | --- | --- || `deployment_name`|string|True|The embedding model deployment name within the same Azure OpenAI resource. || `type`|string|True| Must be `deployment_name`.|
